---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Home" orientation="bottom-left">
  <div class="space-y-3">
    <p>
      Welcome to Oat Café located in the Ākau Tangi Sports Centre in Kilbirnie.
    </p>

    <p>
      At Oat Café, we pride ourselves on being more than just a place to grab a
      quick bite – we are a family-friendly and child-friendly destination where
      friends gather, and memories are made.
    </p>

    <p>
      At Oat Café, you will find real, whole food prepared fresh daily. Our
      casual atmosphere, quality food, friendly staff, and attentive service are
      what we have become known for and keeps our customers coming back and back
      again.
    </p>

    <div class="text-center">
      <p class="curved-underline">We look forward to serving you!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .curved-underline {
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .curved-underline::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    bottom: -8px;
    width: 100%;
    height: 24px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #000;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
</style>
